PRESS DIGEST - Iraq - Jan 3 . These are some of the leading stories in the Iraqi official press on Friday . Reuters has not verified these stories and does not vouch for their accuracy . THAWRA - China condemns so - called no - fly zones in north and south Iraq . - Algeria donates 16 , 500 tonnes of wheat to Iraq . - Revolutionary Command Council issues amnesty to Kurdish servicemen . - Trade ministry to distribute to civil servants some essential foodstuffs with prices 50 percent less than those on commercial market . - A foreign ministry spokesman condemns the Turkish military operation in northern Iraq . - Iraq urges Iran to solve the prisoners of war issue . IRAQ - Border between Iraq and Turkey at Habur has seen wide trade activities . 
